Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:59.42,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}拥抱天宇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.42,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}无尽的痛苦深处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:11.90,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}飘渺的希望初生始动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:19.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}预示指引漫漫前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:23.54,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}你心目中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:27.44,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}唤醒未来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.55,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}破坏 再生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:34.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}诞生 衰亡 进化
